  "texts": [
    "To compute this score, we first calculate the similarity between image s and all the images in the labeled datasets.",
    "The largest value of this similarity is selected as the similarity of image s to the labeled datasets.",
    "A higher Sscore(s) indicates that image s is more dissimilar to the labeled datasets.",
    "We select image s to be included in D L, if it has significant image information and is not redundant with high probability.",
    "We believe that these dissimilar images are more valuable to the current model than other similar images, considering the image information."
